data.description:
This beautiful home is a MUST SEE.  3br, 3bath...open concept living room, dining room and kitchen...stainless appliances, plenty of kitchen cabinet space...large pantry and an upstairs laundry room.
Dining room opens onto windowed deck making it enjoyable for gatherings or just relaxing.  Master bedroom is spacious with tiered ceiling.  Master bath is also spacious with jetted tub, double sinks,  plenty of storage, walk in shower and large walk in closet with lots of shelving and hanging space.  As you go to lower level you see spacious  rec room with wet bar and wine refrigerator and another gathering  space with walk out basement onto an extended patio with under deck ceiling and treed yard making it private spring thru fall.
On lower level is another bath and bedroom with spacious walk in closet.  Lots of storage in unfinished basement side with shelving and small room in case of weather related issues. 
A MUST SEE!!!
